article.headline: Morehead St. 85, Alice Lloyd 51
article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. (AP) -- Kenneth Faried had 24 points and 12 rebounds, both career highs, as Morehead State beat Alice Lloyd of the NAIA 85-51 Monday night. Jamyron Steward added 19 points for Morehead (2-3), and Leon Buchanan and Maze Stallworth scored 15 apiece. Buchanan also had 12 rebounds. Rodney Mitchell led Alice Lloyd (1-7) with 13 points, the team's only player in double figures. Alice took a 2-0 lead with the game's first basket, but it was the team's only lead of the game. Morehead led 39-25 at halftime. Morehead made 52.3 percent of its field goals on 34-of-65 shooting, compared with the opponent's 19-of-25, or 45.2 percent. Morehead also scored 33 points off 28 turnovers by Alice Lloyd. The team's biggest margin was 85-50 with two minutes left to play.
